      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 22 九三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 22 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：賁如濡如，永貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows its subject with the appearance of being adorned and bedewed (with rich favours). But let him ever maintain his firm correctness, and there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
