      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 22 六四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 22 六四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四：賁如皤如，白馬翰如，匪寇婚媾。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth SIX, divided, shows one looking as if adorned, but only in white. As if (mounted on) a white horse, and furnished with wings, (he seeks union with the subject of the first line), while (the intervening third pursues), not as a robber, but intent on a matrimonial alliance.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
